# Meal Planner Skeleton

Simple FastAPI + static HTML/CSS/JS app for trying out Claude subagents & slash commands.

## Layout

```
config_2.0/
├── main.py            # FastAPI app (port 5000)
├── requirements.txt
├── data/
│   ├── meals.json     # Static "DB" of meals
│   └── plan.json      # Weekly plan (updated via API)
└── static/
    ├── index.html
    ├── styles.css
    └── app.js
```

## Run

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py
```

Open http://localhost:5000

## Endpoints

- `GET /`             -> serves `static/index.html`
- `GET /api/meals`    -> list of meals
- `GET /api/plan`     -> current weekly plan
- `PUT /api/plan`     -> `{ "day": "mon", "slot": "lunch", "meal_id": "m5" }`
